<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>관리자 | BMW Plus</title>
<link href="../css/admin.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>
<p id="gotoContents"><a href="#container">본문으로 바로가기</a></p>

<div id="wrapper" class="wrapper">
	<div id="header" class="header">
		<div class="headWrap">
			<img src="../img/@dummy_header.gif" alt="">
		</div>		
	</div><!-- // end header -->
	<hr>
	
	<div id="container" class="container">
		<div id="snb" class="snb">
			<img src="../img/@dummy_snb.gif" alt="">
		</div><!-- // end snb -->
		
		<div id="contents" class="contents">
			<div class="location">
				<a href="#" class="home">HOME</a> > 
				<a href="#">관리자 계정관리</a> > 
				<strong>관리자 계정관리</strong>
			</div>
			
			<h1>관리자 계정관리</h1>
			<h2>관리자 계정추가</h2>
			<p class="tR">* 표는 필수입력 입니다.</p>
			<div class="tableType2 mt10">
				<table>
					<caption>관리자 계정추가</caption>
					<colgroup><col style="width:20%"><col></colgroup>
					<tbody>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">아이디(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="아이디" style="width:250px">
								<a href="#" class="btnS cGray">중복체크</a>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">비밀번호(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="password" title="비밀번호" style="width:250px">
								<p class="txtInfo mt10">비밀번호는 8자 이상으로 영문대소문자, 숫자, 특수문자 중 3가지 이상을 조합하여 주세요.</p>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">비밀번호확인(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="password" title="비밀번호확인" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">계정유형(*)</th>
							<td>
								<select title="계정유형" style="width:250px">
									<option value="">센터(SA)</option>
									<option value="">딜러</option>
								</select>
								<div class="mt10">
									<select title="딜러를 선택하세요" style="width:250px">
										<option value="">딜러를 선택하세요</option>
									</select>
									<select title="센터를 선택하세요" style="width:250px">
										<option value="">센터를 선택하세요</option>
									</select>
								</div>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">계정그룹(*)</th>
							<td>
								<select title="계정그룹" style="width:250px">
									<option value="">컨텐츠관리자</option>
								</select>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">이름(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="이름" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">부서/소속(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="부서/소속" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">담당업무</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="담당업무" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">이메일</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="이메일" placeholder="ex. abc123@bmw.com" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">전화번호(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="전화번호" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr>
							<th scope="row">휴대폰(*)</th>
							<td>
								<input type="text" title="휴대폰" style="width:250px">
							</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>
			<ul class="txtInfo mt10">
				<li>필수항목(*)은 반드시 입력해주세요.</li>
				<li>로그인시 인증문자 발송을 위해 정확한 휴대폰을 입력해 주세요.</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="txtInfo mt10">계정 생성 후에 계정 수정을 통하여 반드시 권한을 입력해주세요.</p>
			<div class="btnBox tR">
				<div class="lBtn"><a href="#" class="btnM cWhite">취소</a></div>
				<a href="#" class="btnM">계정추가</a>
			</div>

		</div><!-- // end contents -->
	</div>

	<div id="footer" class="footer">
		<div class="footArea">
			<p class="copyright">© <strong>BMW Group Korea</strong> All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</div><!-- // end footer -->
	
</div><!-- // end wrapper -->

<!-- script include -->
<script src="../js/jquery-3.1.0.min.js"></script>
<script src="../js/common.js"></script>

</body>
</html>

